-prints/content-2100006&rt=Three+New+Species+of+Neocalyptrocalyx+(Capparaceae)+for+South+America&scisig=AAGBfm2hTXwBcA8rTlH_LfaABXTJKGm1YA>\t <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_share?hl=en&oi=scholaralrt&ss=in&url=https://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/aspt/sb/pre-prints/content-2100006&rt=Three+New+Species+of+Neocalyptrocalyx+(Capparaceae)+for+South+America&scisig=AAGBfm2hTXwBcA8rTlH_LfaABXTJKGm1YA>\t <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_share?hl=en&oi=scholaralrt&ss=fb&url=https://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/aspt/sb/pre-prints/content-2100006&rt=Three+New+Species+of+Neocalyptrocalyx+(Capparaceae)+for+South+America&scisig=AAGBfm2hTXwBcA8rTlH_LfaABXTJKGm1YA>\r\n> [PDF] A new species of Petta (Annelida, Pectinariidae), with comments on Petta assimilis McIntosh, 1885 <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_url?url=https://zookeys.pensoft.net/article/72596/download/pdf/&hl=en&sa=X&d=13225604711119307064&ei=bMuAYazwCdmUy9YP8vmowAQ&scisig=AAGBfm1mpxYU9_2ctzNFUqN_tDoCQMaXYw&oi=scholaralrt&hist=4Z5WABAAAAAJ:10723257300403118941:AAGBfm1inOhnN8aL2qOe-0quNlsVtMjmhA&html=&folt=kw>\r\n> J Zhang, P Hutchings - ZooKeys, 2021\r\n> Abstract The genus Petta Malmgren, 1866 is a small and poorly known genus of the \r\n> annelid family Pectinariidae Quatrefages, 1866. A previous revision of the genus \r\n> found that the type material of the species P. assimilis McIntosh, 1885 had been lost …\r\n>  <https://scholar.google.ca/citations?hl=en&update_op=email_library_add&info=OMH_mWnJircJ&citsig=AMD79ooAAAAAY2H-7HIJTUdnPN7NzrSk9YaTCAqFKS__>\t <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_share?hl=en&oi=scholaralrt&ss=tw&url=https://zookeys.pensoft.net/article/72596/download/pdf/&rt=A+new+species+of+Petta+(Annelida,+Pectinariidae),+with+comments+on+Petta+assimilis+McIntosh,+1885&scisig=AAGBfm2ZeWep_x7BC_xeIAKwZWfBH4osgw>\t <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_share?hl=en&oi=scholaralrt&ss=in&url=https://zookeys.pensoft.net/article/72596/download/pdf/&rt=A+new+species+of+Petta+(Annelida,+Pectinariidae),+with+comments+on+Petta+assimilis+McIntosh,+1885&scisig=AAGBfm2ZeWep_x7BC_xeIAKwZWfBH4osgw>\t <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_share?hl=en&oi=scholaralrt&ss=fb&url=https://zookeys.pensoft.net/article/72596/download/pdf/&rt=A+new+species+of+Petta+(Annelida,+Pectinariidae),+with+comments+on+Petta+assimilis+McIntosh,+1885&scisig=AAGBfm2ZeWep_x7BC_xeIAKwZWfBH4osgw>\r\n> [HTML] Nephtyidae (Annelida: Polychaeta) from the Sea of Marmara and Black Sea, with descriptions of two new species <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_url?url=https://www.mapress.com/zt/article/view/zootaxa.5060.2.2&hl=en&sa=X&d=14000657745695815347&ei=bMuAYazwCdmUy9YP8vmowAQ&scisig=AAGBfm1tgg-BkTA8fSOrBfRxe_6UIbodJw&oi=scholaralrt&hist=4Z5WABAAAAAJ:10723257300403118941:AAGBfm1inOhnN8aL2qOe-0quNlsVtMjmhA&html=&folt=kw>\r\n> S KUŞ, G KURT, ME ÇINAR - Zootaxa, 2021\r\n> The present paper deals with the diversity of nephtyid polychaetes (Nephtyidae) from \r\n> the Sea of Marmara and the Black Sea. Three species belonging to two genera \r\n> (Micronephthys and Nephtys) were found in the Black Sea (coast of Turkey) and six …\r\n>  <https://scholar.google.ca/citations?hl=en&update_op=email_library_add&info=szYFggpUTMIJ&citsig=AMD79ooAAAAAY2H-7JC_CxBmpo5mqK_MMhj3uOTarTIl>\t <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_share?hl=en&oi=scholaralrt&ss=tw&url=https://www.mapress.com/zt/article/view/zootaxa.5060.2.2&rt=Nephtyidae+(Annelida:+Polychaeta)+from+the+Sea+of+Marmara+and+Black+Sea,+with+descriptions+of+two+new+species&scisig=AAGBfm0qCdB-rorSuvd1OWxzTKWcErLi0w>\t <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_share?hl=en&oi=scholaralrt&ss=in&url=https://www.mapress.com/zt/article/view/zootaxa.5060.2.2&rt=Nephtyidae+(Annelida:+Polychaeta)+from+the+Sea+of+Marmara+and+Black+Sea,+with+descriptions+of+two+new+species&scisig=AAGBfm0qCdB-rorSuvd1OWxzTKWcErLi0w>\t <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_share?hl=en&oi=scholaralrt&ss=fb&url=https://www.mapress.com/zt/article/view/zootaxa.5060.2.2&rt=Nephtyidae+(Annelida:+Polychaeta)+from+the+Sea+of+Marmara+and+Black+Sea,+with+descriptions+of+two+new+species&scisig=AAGBfm0qCdB-rorSuvd1OWxzTKWcErLi0w>\r\n> Two new species of Colobomatus Hesse, 1873 (Crustacea: Philichthyidae) parasitic in the interorbital canals of Holocentrus spp.(Holocentriformes: Holocentridae) in … <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_url?url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11230-021-10009-1&hl=en&sa=X&d=5531427322025884984&ei=bMuAYazwCdmUy9YP8vmowAQ&scisig=AAGBfm1hgTlT1BJIq6JPfGDCFWl-o3-T7Q&oi=scholaralrt&hist=4Z5WABAAAAAJ:10723257300403118941:AAGBfm1inOhnN8aL2qOe-0quNlsVtMjmhA&html=&folt=kw>\r\n> JV Couto, F Paschoal - Systematic Parasitology, 2021\r\n> Two new species of parasitic copepods of the genus Colobomatus Hesse, 1873 \r\n> (Cyclopoida) are proposed based on specimens collected from the squirrelfishes \r\n> (Holocentridae) off the coast of Rio de Janeiro, Brazil. Colobomatus luquei n. sp …\r\n>  <https://scholar.google.ca/citations?hl=en&update_op=email_library_add&info=OD0-tteTw0wJ&citsig=AMD79ooAAAAAY2H-7Chu98xWvWUWXAT_gSr1YExc0VPW>\t <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_share?hl=en&oi=scholaralrt&ss=tw&url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11230-021-10009-1&rt=Two+new+species+of+Colobomatus+Hesse,+1873+(Crustacea:+Philichthyidae)+parasitic+in+the+interorbital+canals+of+Holocentrus+spp.(Holocentriformes:+Holocentridae)+in+the+South+Atlantic+Ocean&scisig=AAGBfm3SxnwygePaM-nh7IYtyeE08npxEQ>\t <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_share?hl=en&oi=scholaralrt&ss=in&url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11230-021-10009-1&rt=Two+new+species+of+Colobomatus+Hesse,+1873+(Crustacea:+Philichthyidae)+parasitic+in+the+interorbital+canals+of+Holocentrus+spp.(Holocentriformes:+Holocentridae)+in+the+South+Atlantic+Ocean&scisig=AAGBfm3SxnwygePaM-nh7IYtyeE08npxEQ>\t <https://scholar.google.ca/scholar_share?hl=en&oi=scholaralrt&ss=fb&url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11230-021-10009-1&rt=Two+new+species+of+Colobomatus+Hesse,+1873+(Crustacea:+Philichthyidae)+pa